message: "If you use this software in your research, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "container-net-mirroring"
abstract: >
  A tool that enables Docker containers to observe host-level network traffic
  without the unsafe network_mode: host setting, by configuring Linux Traffic
  Control (tc) mirroring rules from the host into the container's veth interface.
authors:
